  "body": "The install command splits keys on every period, preventing assignment of a key containing the period character. A [RegEx Split](https://golang.org/pkg/regexp/#Regexp.Split) might be a good option to allow for these escaped characters.\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/blob/6b222cdc0fc7d94ce22a265d3a3580cc7afd3cab/cmd/helm/install.go#L271\r\n\r\ne.g. yaml\r\n```\r\n...\r\n    annotations:\r\n{{ toYaml .Values.annotations | indent 6 }}\r\n```\r\n\r\ne.g. command\r\n`--set annotations.iam\\.amazonaws\\.com/role=k8s-logger`\r\n\r\nResult:\r\n```\r\nannotations:\r\n    iam:\r\n        amazonaws:\r\n            com/role: k8s-logger\r\n```\r\n\r\nExpected:\r\n```\r\nannotations:\r\n    iam.amazonaws.com/role: k8s-logger\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
